{"tid":981706,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一個創造互動故嘅app 大家覺得整唔整得過","createTime":"2019-01-14T13:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T17:01:16.000Z","uid":225916,"like":54,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"463c2ed891067b10ae34505277c0755d2b5f528d","tid":981706,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:22:20.000Z","msg":"突然有個idea<br />\n見到咁多人玩互動故<br />\n但事實上我冇信心可以好似其他巴打咁利害<br />\n即場就諗到下一段故事<br />\n<br />\n所以我突然諗到樣野<br />\n如果有個app係咁樣就好啦<br />\n<br />\n純粹分享下 反正我都唔識整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有巴打有興趣整+識得整<br />\n我可以資助少少(最多幾千銀 原諒我搵錢少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n係一個遊戲 自主創作互動故嘅app<br />\n然後故事可以比其他人玩+評分(比玩家之間揀最好睇/最好玩嘅一個故)<br />\n就好似自己揀故事睇咁<br />\n<br />\n其實重點在於創造一個平台俾一堆人一齊玩互動故<br />\n基本上可以話同普通文字系遊戲冇大分別<br />\n但係可以好容易咁寫一個故 主張自己創作<br />\n<br />\n可能有好多人都唔識寫app /冇咁嘅平台<br />\n變相扼殺左好多人嘅創意<br />\n<br />\n大家可以將故事打入去，然後將選項俾選擇大家揀<br />\n示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.mobile01.com/attach/201808/mobile01-fae81a02c880b1de4629443cd3f90ae6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.mobile01.com%2Fattach%2F201808%2Fmobile01-fae81a02c880b1de4629443cd3f90ae6.jpg&h=5178e6fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以加入載圖功能同聲音效果 例如本來個game入面有包背景音樂比人揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又或者有震動畫面嘅功能<br />\n自己創造唔同嘅結局<br />\n<br />\n有興趣嘅話希望可以一齊討論一下<br />\n希望大家唔好屌得咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整得過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整唔過"},{"pid":"2b795ba03e4d3291c8d9f3e588042cbea9c3cb03","tid":981706,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy