8000d86b5ff7c87139d67a7be4c79b4630d402c7","tid":981706,"uid":130776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T14:41:36.000Z","msg":"係咪類似大陸個橙光平臺？"},{"pid":"e0fc7d98fb7999e4d061ba756e6d9fb834445dd5","tid":981706,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8000d86b5ff7c87139d67a7be4c79b4630d402c7","tid":981706,"uid":130776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T14:41:36.000Z","msg":"係咪類似大陸個橙光平臺？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T14:58:30.000Z","msg":"原來已經有類似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過始終都係大陸網<br />\n入面題材都好似一樣樣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部都係 宮廷 戀愛 後宮 <br />\n抄足日本視覺系小說"},{"pid":"1fdc9f2d52f7b41b790c80500eab4f252ccb5e3c","tid":981706,"uid":132326,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:18:11.000Z","msg":"其實個問題係分支分寫勁多野<br />\n得兩個options揀10次要寫1024篇"},{"pid":"92b19e48081c431ab6cf13de518818178a3c7860","tid":981706,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fdc9f2d52f7b41b790c80500eab4f252ccb5e3c","tid":981706,"uid":132326,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:18:11.000Z","msg":"其實個問題係分支分寫勁多野<br />\n得兩個options揀10次要寫1024篇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:31:10.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過可以做到 滿足幾個條件 就跳到某一個章節咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n假設有1 2 3個選擇即係無論你次序係 123 321 132 213 312 231咁<br />\n可能有部分揀錯左就會gameover<br />\n例如有5個選擇會比兇手見到嘅<br />\n而有一個係可以避開兇手咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋可以有好多個結局<br />\n例如一開始有幾條女可以揀做你女朋友 就已經變左3條唔同分線嘅結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能有一部分就係bad ending呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗全部寫到滿嘅"},{"pid":"2ce9200ee1df2d25f060d955db286ec00ccde384","tid":981706,"uid":198900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:35:32.000Z","msg":"Lmgchi"},{"pid":"d22bdfc0a1923d4bb27ae1a741a3ee5ea04bb63d","tid":981706,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:39:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8535b347d9c1b01eb636ff77dab77e04aed2796","tid":981706,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:40:05.000Z","msg":"即係例如話 基本上可以係用返一樣嘅故仔<br />\n所有答案其實都只係去同一條分線咁<br />\n只不過故事嘅內容可以唔同<br />\n但接落黎繼續問嘅都一樣<br />\n<br />\n例如故事係<br />\n<br />\n你選擇要食咩<br />\na.蘋果<br />\nb.橙<br />\n<br />\n如果揀a就會有句 個蘋果好硬<br />\nb就會出現 啲橙好酸<br />\n<br />\n但到最後個game都會繼續向同一個方向發展"},{"pid":"656755fed8b230dd29bf5f98b3d9eb21943a24a4","tid":981706,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:42:10.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以技術支援一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊個話高登好多it9架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deffdf0144838cfaa170dfc9f561b7aa62184ede","tid":981706,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"656755fed8b230dd29bf5f98b3d9eb21943a24a4","tid":981706,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:42:10.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以技術支援一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊個話高登好多it9架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:46:14.000Z","msg":"連登先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌拿星"},{"pid":"4a04d91364c69b2f20f7da59bcb9883e59ed73f9","tid":981706,"uid":96743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:48:56.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"fa91ca50775643ab09b92c0d9a3e9de8b8b2fcc4","tid":981706,"uid":27234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T17:01:16.000Z","msg":"現時其實都有啲互動故app,不過英文居多<br />\n<br />\n有隻手機game叫Lifeline都幾出名，有續集同外傳添<br />\n有中文版，有唔同ending<br />\n寫得好真好immersive<br />\n強烈推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\"